The '''Algic current''' was an underwater current that ranged from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Chad/Legends|Chadra's]] equator to its arctic circle. [[Callista Ming]]'s deep-water ranch followed this current. [[Tsaelke]]s migrated with the current annually.

